trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of data supplied by the <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Especifica el tipo de datos proporcionados por el <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.

trans-unit.source: Represents a dataflow block that is a source of data.
trans-unit.target: Representa un bloque de flujo de datos que es un origen de datos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> of the message being consumed.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> del mensaje que se está usando.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> consuming the message.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> que consume el mensaje.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the message was successfully consumed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si se ha consumido correctamente el mensaje; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by a linked <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> to accept and consume a T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader previously offered by this <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Se llama mediante un <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> vinculado para aceptar y consumir un T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader proporcionado anteriormente por este <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.

trans-unit.source: The value of the consumed message.
trans-unit.target: Valor del mensaje consumido.

trans-unit.source: This may correspond to a different <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> instance than was previously reserved and passed as the <paramref name="messageHeader" /> to <see cref="M:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1.ConsumeMessage(System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader,System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock{`0},System.Boolean@)" />.
trans-unit.target: Esto puede corresponder a una instancia diferente de <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> que se ha reservado y pasado previamente como <paramref name="messageHeader" /> a <see cref="M:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1.ConsumeMessage(System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader,System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock{`0},System.Boolean@)" />.

trans-unit.source: The consuming <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> must use the returned value instead of the value passed as <paramref name="messageValue" /> through <see cref="M:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1.OfferMessage(System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader,`0,System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock{`0},System.Boolean)" />.
trans-unit.target: La interfaz <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> de consumo debe usar el valor devuelto en lugar del valor pasado como <paramref name="messageValue" /> mediante <see cref="M:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1.OfferMessage(System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader,`0,System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock{`0},System.Boolean)" />.

trans-unit.source: If the message requested is not available, the return value will be null.
trans-unit.target: Si el mensaje solicitado no está disponible, el valor devuelto será NULL.

trans-unit.source: Only <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> instances linked to this <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> instance may use <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ConsumeMessage%2A>, and it must only be used to consume <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader> instances previously offered by this source to the target.
trans-unit.target: Solo <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> instancias vinculadas a este <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> instancia puede utilizar <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ConsumeMessage%2A>, y solo debe usarse para consumir <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader> instancias proporcionado anteriormente por este origen al destino.

trans-unit.source: The messageHeader is not valid.
trans-unit.target: messageHeader no es válido.

trans-unit.source: The target is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: El destino es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> to which to connect this source.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> con el que conectar este origen.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowLinkOptions" /> instance that configures the link.
trans-unit.target: Instancia de <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowLinkOptions" /> que configura el vínculo.

trans-unit.source: Links the <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" /> to the specified <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Vincula el <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" /> al <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: An IDisposable that, upon calling Dispose, will unlink the source from the target.
trans-unit.target: IDisposable que, al llamar a Dispose, desvinculará el origen del destino.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="target" /> is null (Nothing in Visual Basic) or <paramref name="linkOptions" /> is null (Nothing in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="target" /> es NULL (Nothing en Visual Basic) o <paramref name="linkOptions" /> es NULL (Nothing en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> of the reserved message being released.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> del mensaje reservado que se va a liberar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> releasing the message it previously reserved.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> que libera el mensaje que reservó previamente.

trans-unit.source: Called by a linked <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> to release a previously reserved <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> by this <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Lo llama una interfaz <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> vinculada para liberar una estructura <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> reservada previamente por esta interfaz <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.

trans-unit.source: Only <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> instances linked to this <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> instance may use `ReleaseReservation`, and it must only be used to release <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader> instances previously and successfully reserved by the target.
trans-unit.target: Solo <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> instancias vinculadas a este <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> instancia puede utilizar `ReleaseReservation`, y solo debe usarse para liberar <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader> instancias previamente y correctamente reservados por el destino.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="messageHeader" /> is not valid.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="messageHeader" /> no es válido.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="target" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor de <paramref name="target" /> es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="target" /> did not have the message reserved.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="target" /> no tiene el mensaje reservado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> of the message being reserved.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> del mensaje que se está reservando.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> reserving the message.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> que reserva el mensaje.

trans-unit.source: Called by a linked <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> to reserve a previously offered <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> by this <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Lo llama una interfaz <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock`1" /> vinculada para reservar una estructura <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader" /> ofrecida previamente por esta interfaz <see cref="T:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock`1" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the message was successfully reserved; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si se ha procesado correctamente el mensaje; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Only <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> instances linked to this <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> instance may use <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ReserveMessage%2A>, and it must only be used to reserve <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader> instances previously offered by this source to the target.
trans-unit.target: Solo <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> instancias vinculadas a este <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601> instancia puede utilizar <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ReserveMessage%2A>, y solo debe usarse para reservar <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.DataflowMessageHeader> instancias proporcionado anteriormente por este origen al destino.

trans-unit.source: If `true` is returned, the <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> must subsequently call either <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ConsumeMessage%2A> or <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ReleaseReservation%2A> for this message.
trans-unit.target: Si `true` se devuelve, el <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ITargetBlock%601> posteriormente debe llamar a <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ConsumeMessage%2A> o <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ReleaseReservation%2A> para este mensaje.

trans-unit.source: Failure to do so may result in the source being unable to propagate any further messages to this or other targets.
trans-unit.target: Si no lo hace puede producir en el origen de su incapacidad para propagar los mensajes adicionales a este u otros destinos.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ReserveMessage%2A> must not be called while the target is holding any internal locks.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow.ISourceBlock%601.ReserveMessage%2A> no debe llamarse mientras mantiene los bloqueos internos en el destino.

trans-unit.source: Doing so will violate the lock hierarchy necessary to avoid deadlocks in a dataflow network.
trans-unit.target: Si lo hace, infringirán la jerarquía de bloqueos necesaria para evitar los interbloqueos en una red de flujo de datos.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="messageHeader" /> is not valid.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="messageHeader" /> no es válido.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="target" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor de <paramref name="target" /> es <see langword="null" />.
